# Direct dev/test dependencies, the human edit surface. Pulls in the
# runtime pins, then adds the test and tooling deps. requirements-dev.txt
# is the compiled, hashed closure.
#
# Starlette's TestClient warns that using httpx rather than httpx2 is
# deprecated (the unit suite prints it once). Migrating to httpx2 is
# deferred; tracked here where the pins live.
-r requirements.in
